# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Client-side environment (Next.js public vars)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# WalletConnect Cloud project id. Enables the WalletConnect connector and
# mobile/QR flows. Get one free at https://cloud.reown.com (formerly
# WalletConnect Cloud). Injected wallets (MetaMask, Rabby) work without it —
# if this is empty the app safely falls back to injected-only.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and set your id:
NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=
